description: The Get VpnclientIpsecParameters operation retrieves information about the vpnclient ipsec policy for P2S client of virtual network gateway in the specified resource group through Network resource provider.

dhgroup.description: The DH Groups used in IKE Phase 1 for initial SA.

sadatasizekilobytes.description: The IPSec Security Association (also called Quick Mode or Phase 2 SA) payload size in KB for P2S client..

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

pfsgroup.description: The Pfs Groups used in IKE Phase 2 for new child SA.

salifetimeseconds.description: The IPSec Security Association (also called Quick Mode or Phase 2 SA) lifetime in seconds for P2S client.

subscription_id.description: The subscription credentials which uniquely identify the Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.
